---
layout: base
title: Labs
permalink: /labs/
---

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-12">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between mb-4">
            <h1 class="h2 fw-bold mb-0">
                <i class="bi bi-mortarboard me-2"></i>Labs
            </h1>
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-primary">
                <i class="bi bi-house me-1"></i>Back to Home
            </a>
        </div>

        <p class="text-muted mb-2">
            Interactive training courses and workshops hosted on the <a href="https://educates.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Educates</a> training platform. Browse courses below, then launch individual workshops directly in your browser.
        </p>
        <p class="text-muted mb-4">
            If you have never used the Educates training platform before, it is recommended you take the walkthrough first so you understand how the platform works.
        </p>

        <div class="alert alert-info mb-4" role="alert">
            <h6 class="alert-heading fw-bold"><i class="bi bi-info-circle me-1"></i>Before you begin</h6>
            <p class="mb-2">
                Access to these workshops is currently free. Depending on demand and hosting costs, this may need to change in the future, or it might just all be shutdown. If you find the workshops valuable and would like to help keep them running, please consider supporting through <a href="https://github.com/sponsors/GrahamDumpleton" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub Sponsors</a>.
            </p>
            <p class="mb-2">
                Workshops run on a shared system with limited capacity. When you launch your first workshop, if there is capacity available you are allocated a time window for doing the workshop and as many follow-up workshops as the time allows. Once that time window expires, you are welcome to come back, but will be subject to checks for available capacity again. Access to the workshops will require you to be authenticated via Github.
            </p>
            <p class="mb-0">
                This platform is still experimental and workshops may occasionally be taken offline for maintenance or updates. If you encounter any issues, please try again later.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Courses Grid -->
<div class="row" id="labsContainer">
    {% for course in labs.courses %}
    {% assign total_workshops = 0 %}
    {% for mod in course.modules %}
        {% assign module_data = labs.modules[mod.file] %}
        {% if module_data.workshops %}
            {% assign total_workshops = total_workshops | plus: module_data.workshops.size %}
        {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
    <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4">
        <article class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm post-list-item">
            <div class="card-body p-4">
                <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
                    <div class="bg-light text-muted rounded-circle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center me-3" style="width: 40px; height: 40px;">
                        <i class="bi bi-mortarboard"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="h5 fw-bold mb-0 flex-grow-1">
                        <a href="/labs/{{ course.slug }}/" class="text-decoration-none stretched-link">
                            {{ course.title }}
                        </a>
                    </h3>
                </div>

                {% if course.description %}
                <div class="text-muted mb-3">{{ course.description | truncate: 200 }}</div>
                {% endif %}

                <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-3">
                    <span class="badge bg-light text-dark border">
                        <i class="bi bi-collection me-1"></i>{{ course.modules.size }} {% if course.modules.size == 1 %}module{% else %}modules{% endif %}
                    </span>
                    <span class="badge bg-light text-dark border">
                        <i class="bi bi-journal-code me-1"></i>{{ total_workshops }} workshops
                    </span>
                </div>

                {% if course.tags and course.tags.size > 0 %}
                <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-1">
                    {% for tag in course.tags limit:4 %}
                    <span class="badge bg-light text-dark border">
                        <i class="bi bi-tag me-1"></i>{{ tag }}
                    </span>
                    {% endfor %}
                </div>
                {% endif %}
            </div>
        </article>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
</div>
